==会议与期刊 ==
该组织每年举办超过80场会议，吸引上万人参加<ref name=embomeeting>{{cite web |url=http://www.the-embo-meeting.org/ |title=The EMBO Meeting |last1=Anon|date=2014 |publisher=European Molecular Biology Organization |archivedate=2014-12-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218065509/http://the-embo-meeting.org/}}</ref>。

